snippet.title: Forgotten Runiverse - Gameplay Preview Video
snippet.description:
Enter a grand fantasy MMORPG full of magic and wonder based on the Forgotten Runes Wizard's Cult NFT collection. The Runiverse is open to anyone - begin your adventure, play, create, own land and earn your place in the pantheon of legends while owning the things you create.

To learn more about Forgotten Runiverse, head to https://runiverse.world/ or follow us on Twitter: https://twitter.com/runiversegame
Sign up on Premint to be among the first to claim your place within the Runiverse: https://www.premint.xyz/forgotten-runiverse/
